entries.femaleVariant: Ehh, no surprise it's generating less. Whole panel's covered in dust.
Should be spending all that time in their labs thinking up ways to stop the storms.
Well, nothin' we can do. Better report it, let 'em send in a cleaning crew.
Yeah, I can see it now. They'll send 'em, they take a few shortcuts, we take all the blame.
Let's just make sure nothing else is damaged.
Yeah, yeah. No need to rush me.
